snippet.title: Dr. Mario DX - Play as Luigi, Daisy and Wario!
snippet.description:
Dr. Mario DX is now available!
A hack that turns the 1990 Game Boy classic into a Game Boy Color game and adds three new playable characters!

Download patch at: https://romhacking.net/hacks/5281/
Alternate download link: https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1tw20biOdNQ7oYMqNw2Aw95409EF4VdMV
